15:52.510 --> 15:54.170
Foreign times lik e these

15:54.346 --> 15:56.421
Life's no life of these

15:56.598 --> 15:58.590
Although I'm no saint

15:58.766 --> 16:00.842
I have no complaint

16:01.018 --> 16:02.810
We must do that task

16:02.979 --> 16:04.852
And it's little enough

16:05.022 --> 16:07.430
They ask:

16:07.608 --> 16:09.565
"Who's Complaining?"

16:09.735 --> 16:11.609
I'm not complaining

16:11.779 --> 16:15.728
You'll see
We'll see this thing through

16:15.908 --> 16:20.071
Because of Axis' trick ery
My coffee now is chicory

16:20.245 --> 16:24.658
